# Title: Potential PowerShell Execution Policy Tampering
# Author: Nasreddine Bencherchali (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2023-01-11
# Level: medium
# Description: Detects changes to the PowerShell execution policy in order to bypass signing requirements for script execution
# MITRE Tactic: Uncategorized
# Tags: attack.defense-impairment
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/registry/registry_set/registry_set_powershell_execution_policy.yml

Details IN ("*Bypass*", "*Unrestricted*") TargetObject IN ("*\\ShellIds\\Microsoft.PowerShell\\ExecutionPolicy", "*\\Policies\\Microsoft\\Windows\\PowerShell\\ExecutionPolicy") NOT (Image IN ("*:\\Windows\\System32\\*", "*:\\Windows\\SysWOW64\\*"))